OL,3,C'Bing, Bing, GONE!': Trump posts AI
OL,4,Cphoto of US ship shooting down Iran
OL,5,Cplane
OL,7,FPresident Donald Trump has posted an
OL,8,FAI-generated photo of a warship
OL,9,Fpainted with a US flag lasering a
OL,10,Fplane with an Iranian flag.
OL,12,FThe photo, posted on Truth Social,
OL,13,Fincluded the caption: "Lasers: Bing,
OL,14,FBing, GONE!!!"
OL,16,FThe post comes as the US military said
OL,17,Fits forces have fired on and disabled
OL,18,Ftwo Iranian oil tankers on Friday,
OL,19,Fhaving exchanged fire with Iranian
OL,20,Fforces in the Strait of Hormuz
OL,21,Fovernight.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
