OL,3,C'Bing, Bing, GONE!': Trump posts AI
OL,4,Cphoto of US ship shooting down Iran
OL,5,Cplane
OL,7,FThe president has insisted that the
OL,8,Fmonth-old ceasefire between the US and
OL,9,FIran is still in place.
OL,11,FWashington is waiting for Iran to
OL,12,Frespond to its latest proposal for a
OL,13,Fdeal to end the war, reopen the strait
OL,14,Fand roll back Tehran's disputed
OL,15,Fnuclear programme.
OL,17,FUS Secretary of State Marco Rubio said
OL,18,Fhe hopes to receive "a serious offer"
OL,19,Ffrom Iran later on Friday.
