OL,7,FThe UAE's defence ministry meanwhile
OL,8,Fsaid three people were wounded after
OL,9,Fair defences engaged two ballistic
OL,10,Fmissiles and three drones launched by
OL,11,FIran. It was not clear if all were
OL,12,Fsuccessfully intercepted.
