OL,3,C'Bing, Bing, GONE!': Trump posts AI
OL,4,Cphoto of US ship shooting down Iran
OL,5,Cplane
OL,7,FIt is not the first time the US
OL,8,Fpresident has used artificial
OL,9,Fintelligence to make photos related to
OL,10,Fthe war with Iran.
OL,12,FIn April, Trump shared a photo of
OL,13,Fhimself wearing aviators and holding a
OL,14,Fgun in front of a backdrop of
OL,15,Fexplosions.
OL,17,FThe image included the strapline "No
OL,18,Fmore Mr Nice Guy!"
